<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-12-03T06:04:02-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-12-03T06:04:02-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-03T06:04:02-05:00</updated><title> Apple Home 对扫地机器人的支持已推迟至 2025 年</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple 徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Kv1Dz6OqKo_3qnOfAppAhpDUW2Y=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73762895/STK071_APPLE_F.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;CHACMj&quot;>;Apple 已悄然推迟了在 HomeKit 中支持扫地机器人的计划。今年早些时候宣布 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/10/24172054/apple-home-homekit-robot-vacuum-support-smart-locks-wwdc24&quot;>;Apple Home iOS 18 终于支持扫地机器人了&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.macrumors.com/2024/12/02/apple-homekit-robot-vacuum-support-2025/&quot;>;MacRumors 已发现 Apple 已更新了其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/home-app/&quot;>;HomeKit 网站&lt;/a>;，指出机器人吸尘器集成要到 2025 年初才会推出。&lt;/p>; &lt; p id=&quot;5qUgoi&quot;>;该网站此前曾提到 HomeKit 将于 2024 年底更新，一些人希望在最初错过了最初的 iOS 18 发布后，机器人吸尘器支持可能会在本月的 iOS 18.2 版本中加入。如果您正在等待 Siri 让机器人真空吸尘器来清洁您的房间，那么您现在必须再坚持几周或几个月。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite >;图片：Apple&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;您很快就能使用...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311885/apple-homekit-robot-vacuums-delayed-2025&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311885/apple-homekit-robot-vacuums-delayed-2025" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311885/apple-homekit-robot-vacuums-delayed-2025</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-03T05:32:11-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-03T05:32:11-05:00</updated><title> One UI 7 中的三星 DeX 应用程序将被微软的 Phone Link 取代</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/cTd9NUkTqpNge8ng2vVLXyXfnjo=/0x0:1920x1280/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73762851 /phonelink.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Microsoft 的 Phone Link 应用程序。&lt;/em>; |图片：微软&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;HlCF15&quot;>;三星即将推出的 One UI 7 更新将不再支持 Windows 上的 DeX 应用程序。 &lt;a 的脚注href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fuk%2Fapps%2Fsamsung-dex%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theve rge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F12%2F3%2F24311882%2Fsamsung-dex-app-windows-replaced-link-to-windows-microsoft-phone-link&quot; rel=&quot;poned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;三星英国网站&lt;/a>;，由 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.androidauthority.com/samsung-dex-support-ends-3504306/&quot;>; 发现&lt;em>;Android Authority&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 透露，DeX PC 应用程序“将终止对 One UI 7 版本的支持”，三星鼓励用户使用“链接到 Windows”功能，而不是利用与Windows 上的 Microsoft Phone Link 应用程序。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;DOsV6Y&quot;>;适用于 Windows 的 DeX 应用程序，不要与可让您的&lt;a href=&quot;https://insights.samsung. com/2024/08/26/the-beginners-guide-to-samsung-dex-13/&quot;>;手机连接到电脑&lt;/a>;，让您将手机屏幕镜像到电脑，并轻松地在电脑之间拖放文件设备。它与 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/3/31/23004352/microsoft-phone-link-rebranding-windows-11-design-update&quot;>;Microsoft 的 Phone Link 应用&lt;/ a>;，三星和微软近年来在这方面密切合作，因此三星青睐是有道理的......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311882/samsung-dex-app-windows-replaced-link-to-windows-microsoft-phone-link&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a >; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311882/samsung-dex-app-windows-replaced-link-to-windows-microsoft-phone-link" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311882/samsung-dex-app-windows-replaced-link-to-windows-microsoft-phone-link</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-03T05:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-03T05:00:00-05:00</updated><title>数据经纪人可能被禁止出售您的社会安全号码</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;挂锁和链条旁边的像素化钥匙插图，暗示在线数据安全。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/R4MjSj6krABAZqVnYCl9SJymHZI=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x8 73/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73762823/STK453_Privacy_D_CVirginia.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Cath Virginia / The Verge |照片：Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;vBDsn0&quot;>;在影响数亿美国人的备受瞩目的黑客攻击之后，消费者金融保护局 (CFPB) 提出了一项限制数据经纪人的规则&#39; 出售美国人敏感个人和财务信息的能力。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;rd0yyn&quot;>;根据拟议规则，出售有关消费者收入、信用记录、信用评分或债务支付信息的数据经纪人将被禁止考虑消费者报告机构。因此，他们必须遵守《公平信用报告法》(FCRA)，该法律限制这些机构获取和使用消费者报告中提供的信息的方式。换句话说，他们将被视为信用局和背景调查公司，它们已经必须遵守 FCRA。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;aKmiXE&quot;>;在...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311498/cfpb-rule-data-brokers-social-security-number-fico-score&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311498/cfpb-rule-data-brokers-social-security-number-fico-score" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/3/24311498/cfpb-rule-data-brokers-social-security-number-fico-score</id><author><name>盖比·德尔·瓦莱</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-03T00:58:32-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-03T00:58:32-05:00</updated><title>您仍然可以购买网络星期一最后一刻的最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;浏览器窗口中排列的网络星期一销售产品的插图。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/eN-C8Y4oBM5R56F-wkCPw4_952g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cd n.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73756741/247350_CMBF_2024_EWinatacyberMonday.6.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Elen Winata for The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;还有一些时间可以节省购买各种 Verge 认可的商品，